## Helper command

```
./harness start                  # begin a new iteration (coordinator)
./harness implement <task-id>    # resume an in-progress task (implementer)
./harness status                 # show CURRENT.md + active brief
./harness end                    # archive completed task → idle
./harness remember "<text>"      # append entry to MEMORY.md
./harness curate-memory          # quarterly MEMORY.md cleanup
```

See [harness](harness).
